data.description: Important - Seller to find suitable housing and is actively looking.   Almost new Roof, In law quarters or rental opportunity in the basement with 2 Beds and its own full kitchen with butcher block counter tops. New paint outside, along with a concrete patio with a built in fire pit. Come take a look today and don't let the opportunity pass you buy for this great home in the Lower Dauphin School District.   Come and take a look at this large home with approximately 3200 square feet of living space, 6 total bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms and a half bath along with a 4-car attached garage. This property is perfect for the large family or someone looking for a home with in-law quarters as well. The main level has 4 bedrooms, and the lower level has 2 bedrooms, a full bath, a full kitchen and a large living room area. Don't wait schedule your showing today on this updated home. This is an opportunity to own a large unique home in Lower Dauphin School district. Would be perfect for two families or a large family. With the Full kitchen upstairs, and a full kitchen downstairs it has plenty of space. PROFESSIONAL PHOTOS TAKEN AND WILL UPLOAD AS SOON AS THEY ARE RECIEVED.
